OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775761868
OL,3,CFour people die crossing English
OL,4,CChannel in small boat
OL,6,FTwo men and two women have died after
OL,7,Fattempting to cross the English
OL,8,FChannel in a small boat.
OL,10,FConfirming the deaths at a news
OL,11,Fconference, prefect of Pas-de-Calais,
OL,12,FFrancois-Xavier Lauch, said the people
OL,13,Fwere swept away by "dangerous"
OL,14,Fcurrents after "attempting to board a
OL,15,Fwater-taxi".
OL,17,FOne migrant suffering from hypothermia
OL,18,Fwas treated for minor injuries,
OL,19,Faccording to local media, while 37
OL,20,Fother people were rescued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
