OL,3,CFour people die crossing English
OL,4,CChannel in small boat
OL,6,FAuthorities said that the boat
OL,7,Fcontinued its journey towards Britain
OL,8,Fwith around 30 migrants on board.
OL,10,FThis is a breaking news story - more
OL,11,Fto follow.
